# Twitter
Twitter analysis report
# Twitter Data
The current model has two files, one is for collecting data from twitter and adding it to an SQL object.
The other is for collecting the data and analyzing the data.
# Data collection
the model autheticates to the twitter api and collects tweets on trending Kenyan topics

# Data Analysis
the model uses the NLTK tools to analyze the tweets and create some visualizations in word cloud and line plots

# Model

The analysis creates a Gradient boosting machine learning model to predict the topic of the tweet.
the model used is a classsification model that predicts if a tweet falls under 3 topics: "social","media","politics"

The model achieves an accuracy rate of 80% so its an overall good model that can predict the topic of the tweet with 80% accuracy.


